name: Tribute to Dischi Egede
description: Looped animation based on the iconic geometric cover element of the production music LPs of the Dischi Egede record label. A happy combination of hand crafted vectors with a generative line treatment applied as a post-production effect, this method of traditional techniques combined with algorithmic process feels a fitting tribute to the music of the label. | 1024 x 1024 | @notyetmeasured | measureless.io
